headline: Franklin Templeton Launches Franklin Dividend Growth ETF (FRIZ)
summary: SAN MATEO, Calif., August 29, 2025--Franklin Templeton today announced the launch of the Franklin Dividend Growth ETF (NYSE: FRIZ), an actively managed exchange-traded fund designed to seek long-term capital appreciation by investing in financially sound, primarily U.S. based firms that have the potential to generate consistent dividend increases.
